title: “Summer of Kunt” (w/ Sudi Green)
itunes:title: “Summer of Kunt” (w/ Sudi Green)
description:
This episode marks a SEA CHANGE in the LCU - and you’re just going to have to listen to the end to find out why! (It involves a “diva moment” from one of our esteemed hosts…)

But first, fan favorite Sudi Green is back - and just in time to make some Summer resolutions. It will be a Summer about loving oneself, about opening up creatively, and about finding a man with no roommates to worship your body. And of course Matt and Bo dive into pop culture, tackling Kelly Clarkson, Nicki Minaj, Demi Lovato (and her consistent vibrato), and much much more. “Voice MemOH, You Bitch” from Christi Chiello.
